snippet.title: Super Smash Bros. - Adventure Luigi
snippet.description:
This is the classic adventure mode from Super Smash Bros. for the Nintendo 64 played with Luigi on Very Hard.

This is the original Super Smash Bros. from the Nintendo 64. This adventure mode is called the classic mode in the future editions of the Smash Series.

Thanks for watching and subscribe for more Super Smash Bros.

Played by Maurits.
